SUMMARY:ABC13 Loves Teachers
DTSTAMP:20260701T101457Z
DTSTART:20260731T060000Z
DESCRIPTION:ABC13 and their community partners are coming together to stuff
	 school buses with school supplies to benefit Houston Food Bank’s School P
	rograms! On the date of the supply drive day\, Channel 13 will broadcast l
	ive from the station to tell the story of the program\, how it impacts ama
	zing teachers and students\, and to encourage people to donate. Channel 13
	 will do interviews with teachers\, schools and students to tell their sto
	ry of how the program helps them and why it is important. These interviews
	 will run in advance of the drive date and also during the event date.\n\n
	https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/abc13-loves-teachers/\n\nFro
	m Houston Food Bank
URL:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/abc13-loves-teachers/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:houston-food-bank
CATEGORIES:Houston Food Bank
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT12H
