DTSTAMP:20260701T101457Z
DTSTART:20260912T130000Z
DESCRIPTION:Help HFB make change for better lives by participating in this 
	special volunteer experience where you’ll build advocacy skills to help ad
	dress what is driving hunger and poverty. The shift begins with interactiv
	e dialogue that empowers you to influence decisions affecting your communi
	ty and transitions into a collaborative volunteer task. \nRegister Here\n\
	nhttps://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/beyond-the-box-volunteer-sh
	ift-3/\n\nFrom Houston Food Bank
